parameters.name: Start_Year
parameters.description:
The Start_Year field identifies the year of the beginning of the       
                        particular segment.

parameters.name: Start_DDOY
parameters.description:
The Start_DDOY field identifies the decimal day of year of the beginning
                        of the particular segment.

parameters.name: End_Year
parameters.description:
The Start_Year field identifies the year at the end of the particular  
                        segment.

parameters.name: End_DDOY
parameters.description:
The Start_DDOY field identifies the decimal day of year at the end of   
                        the particular segment.

parameters.name: Segment_Name
parameters.description: A description of the particular segment.
